  "short_description": "USR is a 3rd person platformer, that takes gaming back to the basics. The idea is simple... a single player, assault-course game. Easy to learn, hard to master. Where timing is everything, and nothing is down to 'chance'. Take the test... be the best, be the USR Champion!",
